data.description: This lovely split-level home set in a charming neighborhood offering shady streets and spacious lots is ready for new owners! The main living floor plan and vaulted ceilings provide a bright, open, airy, and comfortable entertaining space. Three bedrooms and two bathrooms are located on the same floor as the main living space. The lower level of the home showcases a spacious flex room, additional playroom, workout room or office space, laundry space, and an unfinished storage area. You will simply fall in love with the large deck and wooded lot with plenty of backyard to enjoy!
